  "subject": "Add inventory endpoint to retrieve CM handle by reference",
  "commit_message": "Add inventory endpoint to retrieve CM handle by reference\n\n- New OpenAPI endpoint GET /ncmpInventory/v1/ch?distinguishedName={fdn}\n- Cm-handle-id also supported (instead of fdn)\n- Controller method reusing existing facade and mapper\n- Refactored yaml\n    common parameters defined once in components\n    use paths: defining multiple operations under same path (for /ch)\n- Updated readme with instructions on how to ignore ProvMnS Jar (cannot use .gitIgnore for a file we want to keep in our repo)\n- Updated postman collection\n    added example for new method get method by FDN\n    added example for legacy data get using alt-id\n- Fixed some legacy issues with responses in yaml\n\nIssue-ID:CPS-3210\n\nChange-Id: I81e09e4faef566fbfb6d578b97f01ba9c070847d\nSigned-off-by: ToineSiebelink <toine.siebelink@est.tech>\n",
